 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 6. the fan of salsa is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is between the person who's birthday is in april and the owner of the bird##2
 8. the fan of pop is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | collecting | hiking     | puzzles  | magic-tricks |
